title: Fantasy Pancakeswap
body:
It’s a tournament that players select a combination of pools and attribute a porcentaje of importance. 

It’s like having a fictional USB$100 and invested them in different pools and see who gets more profits in a week. 

Then in a week the person that selected the most profitable combination regarding rewards by the change in APY in that week would win a price.

It’s like fantasy baseball but with pools in the pancakeswap ecosystem.
